  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the sensitivity and specificity of the CTLM system
      when used adjunctively with mammography compared to mammography alone in the heterogeneously
      and extremely dense breast population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
